title: Episode 11 w/ the Drink Champs Family
itunes:title: Episode 11 w/ the Drink Champs Family
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN drink it up with some friends and family in this bonus Drink Champs episode. Aside from the regular Drink Champs associates they are also joined by DJ/producer Scram Jones and celebrity promoter Mr. Lee. WARNING: Don't listen to this episode (or any of them for that matter) with your kids! --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
